{"tid":1947600,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"正式宣佈 香港已經輸咗了","createTime":"2020-03-28T11:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T11:58:41.000Z","uid":237459,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"671403c77419803e8b513059fd937b6331c0deee","tid":1947600,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全球金融中心排名，香港跌出三甲。<br />\n<br />\n《全球金融中心指數》報告由英國一間智庫及深圳綜合開發研究院發布。香港在指數的得分大跌34分，排名跌至第6位，較去年9月下跌3位。紐約及倫敦繼續位列榜首及第二，緊隨其後有東京、上海及新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，今次報告中各個金融中心的排名較之前變化更大，反映國際貿易不確定及地緣政治和動盪事件影響；又解釋香港得分的下降幅度較前五名更為顯著，是受到去年社會事件影響，指事件為香港帶來前所未有的挑戰。"},{"pid":"2807df8184ee04aec146f849cd29c049857bb556","tid":1947600,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">深圳綜合開發研究院發布</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e7080887aa418ed6bd91f3cfdb378e9869338832","tid":1947600,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2807df8184ee04aec146f849cd29c049857bb556","tid":1947600,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">深圳綜合開發研究院發布</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔使大大隻紅字，你唔係應該好開心咩，終於攬炒成功"},{"pid":"ad1a7d46f8e506f1be69d1663af4545945764e8c","tid":1947600,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"就係因為係金融中心先要比支那控制<br />\n寧願唔好做！"},{"pid":"b5d99dc0e3c20b5a4928b6fc461226bfda5b6b76","tid":1947600,"uid":174207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2807df8184ee04aec146f849cd29c049857bb556","tid":1947600,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">深圳綜合開發研究院發布</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T1